Package dev.siroshun.event4j.api.listener

Interface ListenerSubscriber<K,E,O>

Type Parameters:
K - the key type
E - the event type
O - the order type
@NotNullByDefault public interface ListenerSubscriber<K,E,O>
An interface to subscribe/unsubscribe listeners.

This interface can also be used to get existing listeners.
